#

Install Vundle for vim (additional bundles for vim)
https://github.com/gmarik/vundle

Install YouCompleteMe for vim (auto-complete for vim)
https://github.com/Valloric/YouCompleteMe

Install Syntastic for vim (syntax checker for vim)
https://github.com/scrooloose/syntastic

sudo apt-get install mailutils sharutils mutt exim4 (for command-line mail features)

Install python auto-complete for vim
https://github.com/davidhalter/jedi-vim

Install commonly used tools like 'perf'
sudo apt-get install linux-tools-common

Install 'fugitive' a nice wrapper for git in vim
https://github.com/tpope/vim-fugitive 

Install NFS common 
sudo apt-get install nfs-common 

Automatically update your 'tags' file (generated by ctags) on file update in vim
https://github.com/craigemery/dotFiles/blob/master/vim/plugin/autotag.vim

Install distcc for faster builds
https://code.google.com/p/distcc/
